The '''Bet's Off''' was a somewhat elegant [[Tapcafe/Legends|tapcafe]] that was located on the [[Jubilee Wheel (space station)|''Jubilee Wheel'']], which contained a number of [[Sabacc/Legends|sabacc]] tables. During the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]], [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] visited the place while on the ''Wheel'', where he had a rather unpleasant encounter with [[Bossk/Legends|Bossk]].

